name: .IXA File Extension
summary: Learn about .IXA files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: DVD disc image file created with Ulead disc authoring software; saved in a proprietary format readable only by Ulead applications, such as DVD Workshop, DVD Movie Factory, and Copy.Now.

content: IXA files can be burned with the Ulead Disc Image Recorder, which is included with Ulead DVD PictureShow, VideoStudio, and MediaStudio Pro.
Ulead is owned by the Corel Corporation.
